<div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
  <div style="width:3rem; height:3rem; background:#f0fdf4; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin:0 auto 0.75rem;">
    <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="font-size:1.4rem; color:#16a34a;"></i>
  </div>
  <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; color:#18181b; margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Convite criado!</h2>
  <p style="font-size:0.83rem; color:#71717a; margin:0;">Compartilhe o link abaixo com <strong style="color:#18181b;"><%= @invited_user.name %></strong>.</p>
</div>

<div style="background:#f4f4f5; border-radius:8px; padding:0.75rem 1rem; margin-bottom:1rem; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;">
  <input id="invite-url" type="text" readonly value="<%= @invite_url %>"
         style="flex:1; border:none; background:transparent; font-size:0.78rem; color:#374151; outline:none; min-width:0; word-break:break-all;" />
  <button onclick="copyInviteUrl()" id="copy-btn"
          style="flex-shrink:0; background:#18181b; color:#fff; border:none; border-radius:6px; padding:0.4rem 0.85rem; font-size:0.78rem; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; white-space:nowrap;">
    Copiar
  </button>
</div>

<div style="background:#eff6ff; border:1px solid #bfdbfe; border-radius:8px; padding:0.6rem 0.9rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; font-size:0.78rem; color:#1d4ed8; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
  <i class="bi bi-send" style="flex-shrink:0; margin-top:1px;"></i>
  <span>Cole este link no WhatsApp, e-mail ou outra mensagem e envie diretamente para o colaborador.</span>
</div>
<div style="background:#fffbeb; border:1px solid #fde68a; border-radius:8px; padding:0.6rem 0.9rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; font-size:0.78rem; color:#92400e; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
  <i class="bi bi-clock" style="flex-shrink:0; margin-top:1px;"></i>
  <span>O link expira assim que for utilizado. Gere um novo se necessário.</span>
</div>
<div style="background:#f4f4f5; border-radius:8px; padding:0.6rem 0.9rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:0.75rem; color:#71717a; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
  <i class="bi bi-eye-slash" style="flex-shrink:0; margin-top:1px;"></i>
  <span>Não compartilhe o link publicamente — qualquer pessoa com ele pode criar uma conta.</span>
</div>

<div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem;">
  <%= link_to "Novo convite", new_invitation_path,
        style: "flex:1; text-align:center; background:#fff; color:#18181b; border:1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius:8px; padding:0.6rem; font-size:0.84rem; font-weight:500; text-decoration:none;" %>
  <%= link_to "Voltar para Usuários", users_path,
        style: "flex:1; text-align:center; background:#18181b; color:#fff; border:none; border-radius:8px; padding:0.6rem; font-size:0.84rem; font-weight:500; text-decoration:none;" %>
</div>

<script>
  function copyInviteUrl() {
    var input = document.getElementById("invite-url");
    var btn   = document.getElementById("copy-btn");
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(input.value).then(function() {
      btn.textContent = "Copiado!";
      btn.style.background = "#16a34a";
      setTimeout(function() {
        btn.textContent = "Copiar";
        btn.style.background = "#18181b";
      }, 2000);
    });
  }
</script>
